stabilised.

G82328 (2) -> OMwrite sin(x)

   (2)
  "<OMOBJ>
  <OMA>
    <OMS cd="transc1" name="sin"/>
    <OMV name="x"/>
  </OMA>
</OMOBJ>
"

Mike.

